<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV100">
<l>piṟappiṉōṭu pēriṭarc cuḻikkaṇniṉṟu nīṅkumaḵ</l>
<l>tiṟappavaitta ñāṉanīca raikkaraikko ṭēṟṟumā</l>
<l>peṟaṟkariya niṉṉapāta pattiyāṉa pācaṉam</l>
<l>peṟaṟkariya māyaṉē yeṉakkunalka vēṇṭumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O hard-to-obtain, wonderful [Lord]! You should grant me the boat that is bhakti</l>
<l>For Your feet, which is hard to obtain,</l>
<l>Which is the means that lifts up to the banks [even] people with petty knowledge</l>
<l>who cause that which [ensures] leaving the eddy that is a great calamity, along with</l>
<l rend="indent">births, to be beyond [one’s reach].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
